  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, 2 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Slice <strong>half </strong>your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> as thinly as you can, then add them to the bowl and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1675071560714-x200.jpg",
