    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the black beans have softened, add a small knob of <strong>butter</strong> to the pot and mash them to a coarse paste – these are your <strong>refried beans</strong></p><p>Drain the <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong>, discard the liquid</p>",
